import React, {Component} from 'react' import moment from 'moment' import './Table.css' const Table = props => { // curPrice & USD are from live API const { purchaseDate, name, symbol, amountPurchased, purchasePrice, curPrice: { USD } }= props return(
Date Time Name Symbol
{moment(purchaseDate).format("MM/DD/YY")}
{moment(purchaseDate).format("hh:mma")}
{name}
{symbol}
{amountPurchased}
{purchasePrice}
{USD}
) } export default Table;
